Revision history for Alien::JPCRE2.

0.010000 2017-11-08

	- Fix Bug, BSD & MacOSX, Change 'std::setlocale' To 'setlocale'
		Upgrade To JPCRE2 v10.31.02-DEV Unofficial
	- Require Alien::PCRE2 v0.014

0.009000 2017-10-31 Codename Vulcan

    - HOLIDAY EDITION: Happy Halloween!
    - Upgrade To JPCRE2 v10.31.01 Official

0.008000 2017-07-25

    - Properly Require Test2::Suite & Test2::V0, Part 2 (Thanks Grinnz)
    - Compatibility With Older Versions Of ExtUtils::MakeMaker (Thanks Grinnz)

0.007000 2017-07-25

    - Windows, Properly Require Alien::gmake & Alien::MSYS
    - Properly Require Test2::Suite & Test2::V0
    - Require Alien::PCRE2 v0.013 For Bug Fixes

0.006000 2017-07-21

    - Windows, Enable -DPCRE2_STATIC Macro To Fix Build Errors

0.005000 2017-07-20

    - Disable C++11 Features, Support Older Compilers
    - Test Suite, Remove t/02_make_check.t, Move `make check` To alienfile
    - Require Alien::PCRE2 v0.012
    - Test Suite, Begin Upgrade To Test::Alien

0.004000 2017-07-13

    - Alien::PCRE2 Dependency, Require At Configure Time

0.003000 2017-07-13

    - Test Suite, Skip `make check` On System Install
    - Require Alien::Build v0.60 For Bug Fixes
    - Alien::PCRE2 Dependency, Remove Hard-Coded Installer Code
    - Update alienfile To Use Proper Plugins (Thanks plicease)

0.002000 2017-07-04

    - Remove Extraneous Debugging Output

0.001000 2017-07-03

    - Initial Release!
    - Linux Support
